    <div class="card"><div class="sh"><div class="shdot" style="background:var(--lime)"></div>Strategy</div>
      <div class="strat-c on" id="st-av" onclick="setSt('avalanche')"><div class="strat-nm">🔥 Avalanche <span class="bdg bdg-p">SAVES MOST</span></div><div class="strat-d">Extra payment targets highest-interest debt first. Optimal mathematically.</div></div>
      <div class="strat-c" id="st-sn" onclick="setSt('snowball')"><div class="strat-nm">⛄ Snowball <span class="bdg bdg-muted">MOTIVATING</span></div><div class="strat-d">Clears smallest balance first. Psychological momentum.</div></div>
      <div class="div"></div><div id="dbt-callout"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
